      "content": "<objective>COMPREHENSIVE SYNTHESIS: Compile ALL research findings from the 5 parallel investigations into a single structured report. This report will be consumed by advisor/analyst agents to design the hard restructuring phases.</objective>\n\nWorking directory: /Users/apple/hivemind-plugin-private\n\nRead these files for raw data:\n1. .planning/research/opencode-sdk-v1155-api-audit-2026-05-21.md (SDK API audit)\n2. .planning/codebase/DI-ARCHITECTURE-ANALYSIS.md (DI/architecture analysis)\n3. .planning/codebase/CONCERNS.md (current concerns)\n4. .planning/codebase/ARCHITECTURE.md (architecture)\n5. .planning/phases/17-sync-boundary-definition-src-audit-and-cleanup/17-FINDINGS.md (dead code findings)\n6. .planning/archive/ (architectural history)\n\nAlso use these grep commands for real-time verification:\n```bash\n# Check dist/ stale files\nls dist/features/steering-engine/ 2>/dev/null\nls dist/features/bootstrap/runtime-detection/ 2>/dev/null\nls dist/hooks/transforms/toggle-gates.ts 2>/dev/null  \nls dist/task-management/recovery/ 2>/dev/null\n\n# Check sync fs call distribution\nrg -c \"readFileSync|writeFileSync|mkdirSync|existsSync|readdirSync|renameSync\" src/ --type ts | sort -t: -k2 -rn | head -20\n\n# Check throw new Error distribution  \nrg -c \"throw new Error\" src/ --type ts | sort -t: -k2 -rn | head -20\n\n# Check legacy/deprecated distribution\nrg -c \"legacy|deprecated\" src/ --type ts -i | sort -t: -k2 -rn | head -15\n\n# Check unused deps grep\nfor pkg in commander diff fast-glob fast-xml-parser ink js-yaml jsonc-parser node-pty tree-sitter-javascript vscode-jsonrpc web-tree-sitter; do echo \"=== $pkg ===\"; rg \"from.*['\\\"]$pkg\" src/ --type ts; done\n\n# Check factory vs class pattern count\necho \"Factory functions (createXxx):\" && rg -c \"export function create\" src/ --type ts | awk -F: '{sum+=$2} END {print sum}'\necho \"Class exports:\" && rg -c \"export class\" src/ --type ts | awk -F: '{sum+=$2} END {print sum}'\necho \"Direct const exports:\" && rg -c \"^export (const|let|var)\" src/ --type ts | awk -F: '{sum+=$2} END {print sum}'\n```\n\nWrite a comprehensive report to `.planning/research/hard-restructuring-synthesis-2026-05-21.md` containing:\n\n## Section 1: SDK/Plugin Interface Mismatches\nFrom the OpenCode SDK audit, what are the exact mismatches between Hivemind implementation vs SDK contracts?\n\n## Section 2: Dependency/Injection Architecture\nFrom DI-ARCHITECTURE-ANALYSIS.md and raw grep, what are the consistent vs inconsistent factory patterns? What are the 5 anti-patterns?\n\n## Section 3: Package.json Dependency Audit\nWhich deps are unused (can be removed)? Which need minor bumps? Which need major bumps (deferred)?\n\n## Section 4: Dead Code + Stale Dist\nWhat dead code remains in src/ that Phase 18 didn't cover? What stale files exist in dist/?\n\n## Section 5: Legacy/Deprecation Burden\nHow many legacy references, sync fs calls, throw Error sites, and where are they concentrated?\n\n## Section 6: Architectural Anti-Patterns from Archive History\nFrom the archive analysis, what recurring failure patterns exist?\n\n## Section 7: Severity Classification\nClassify each finding as:\n- 🔴 CRITICAL — blocks correctness, causes runtime failures, security\n- 🟡 HIGH — architectural debt that compounds over time\n- 🟠 MEDIUM — code quality, test gaps, minor inconsistency\n- ⚪ INFO — documentation, observability\n\nFocus on findings that have concrete file:line references and evidence commands.\n",
